quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  10,62,"Mosakaika! Ndithudi abwenzi a Mulungu ndipo amamukonda Iye kwambiri, sadzakhala ndi mantha ndiponso sadzadandaula"
  10,63,Iwo amene adakhulupirira ndipo anali kuopa Mulungu
  10,64,Kwa iwo ndi chisangalalo m’dziko lino ndiponso m’dziko limene lili n’kudza. Palibe kusintha kulikonse m’Mau a Mulungu. Kumeneko ndiko kupambana kwakukulu
  10,65,Ndipo mawu awo asakukhumudwitse iwe. Ndithudi mphamvu zonse Mwini wake ndi Mulungu. Iye ndi wakumva ndi wodziwa
  10,66,Mosakaika! Ndithudi Mulungu ndiye mwini wa zimene zili kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi. Ndipo onse amene amapembedza milungu yabodza satsatira china chilichonse koma zinthu zopanda pake ndipo iwo amangopeka mabodza
  10,67,Iye ndiye amene adakupangirani usiku kuti muzipumula ndi usana kuti muziona. Ndithudi mu izi muli zizindikiro kwa anthu amene amamva
  10,68,"Iwo amanena kuti: “Mulungu wabereka mwana wamwamuna.” Mulungu ayeretsedwe ndi zimenezo. “Iye ndi Wolemera. Zake ndi zonse zimene zili m’lengalenga ndi padzikolapansi. Paichiinumulibeumboni. Kodimukunena zinthu zokhudza Mulungu zimene simuzidziwa?”"
  10,69,"Nena, “Ndithudi iwo amene amapeka bodza lokhudza Mulungu sadzapambana ayi.”"
  10,70,Chisangalalo cha kanthawi kochepa ka m’dziko lapansi ndipo ndi kwa Ife kumene adzabwerera ndipo Ife tidzawalawitsa chilango chowawa chifukwa cha kukana kwawo